    methodTitle: "Aleke tsitsim mɔnu wɔna agbeli si nyona",
    methodP1: "Tsitsim mɔnu, si Dr. Howard Bradbury tso Australian National University wɔ, nye tekiniki bɔbɔe gake si dɔa dɔ si ɖea cyanide si le agbeli wɔ me ɖe anyigba ŋutɔ. Mɔnu sia zãa enzyme ƒe dɔwɔwɔ si le agbeli ati me ko. Ne agbeli ƒe akpawo fu la, enzyme si woyɔna be linamarase do go linamarin (glucoside cyanogenic), gbãna eŋu eye ɖe mlɔeba me eɖea hydrogen cyanide gas ayi, si ate ŋu ahu ɖe dedie.",
